{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778991803314,"sessionID":"ses_1cbe49278ffeRFVub9JhoaSOUZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_dB6iK1BP4zTtVHD6FcPJHSVx","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Summary:\n+- corrected EC-driven parentage for a batch of oxidoreductase activity terms in the catalytic activity branch\n+- updated several reaction definitions to align with current RHEA reactions\n+- renamed terms where the existing label no longer matched the enzyme class/reaction\n+\n+Validated locally with `make travis_build`.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+This PR addresses issue #31969 by correcting a batch of oxidoreductase catalytic activity terms whose asserted parentage did not match their EC subclass, and by updating several reaction definitions/labels to better align with RHEA.\n+\n+Main changes\n+\n+- Reparented EC:1.17.1 terms to `GO:0016726` and the EC:1.17.2 term to `GO:0016725`:\n+  - `GO:0008863` formate dehydrogenase (NAD+) activity\n+  - `GO:0047899` formate dehydrogenase (NADP+) activity\n+  - `GO:0008839` 4-hydroxy-tetrahydrodipicolinate reductase activity\n+  - `GO:0047111` formate dehydrogenase (cytochrome-c-553) activity\n+\n+- Corrected CH-OH / CH-CH / CH-NH branch placement:\n+  - `GO:0050607` reparented to `GO:0016616` and renamed to `S-(hydroxymethyl)mycothiol dehydrogenase activity`\n+  - `GO:0008762` reparented to `GO:0016628`\n+  - `GO:0018525` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+  - `GO:0044684` reparented to `GO:0016645`\n+  - `GO:0033717` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+\n+- Corrected oxygenase/dioxygenase parentage in the 1.14 branch:\n+  - `GO:0102394` renamed to `L-isoleucine 4-hydroxylase activity` and reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0047081` renamed to `3-hydroxy-2-methylpyridine-5-carboxylate monooxygenase [NAD(P)H] activity` and reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0106145` reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0010277` reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0050588` reparented to `GO:0016702`\n+  - `GO:0033759`, `GO:0045431`, `GO:0047594`, `GO:0050589` reparented to `GO:0050498`\n+  - `GO:0102717` reparented from `GO:0050498` to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0050616` and `GO:0102915` reparented to `GO:0016717`\n+  - `GO:0032441`, `GO:0004498`, and `GO:0036199` reparented to `GO:0016713`\n+  - `GO:0018570` reparented to `GO:0016708`\n+\n+- Updated reaction definitions to current RHEA-aligned wording where requested, including:\n+  - `GO:0050607`, `GO:0008762`, `GO:0018525`, `GO:0044684`, `GO:0047081`, `GO:0106145`, `GO:0102717`, `GO:0050616`, `GO:0102915`, `GO:0032441`\n+\n+- Added `term_tracker_item` links to issue `#31969` on all edited terms.\n+\n+Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before edits:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+\n+- Post-edit validation:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+  - `robot reason -r ELK -i go-edit.obo -o /tmp/opencode/go-edit.reasoned.obo` passed\n+  - `make travis_build` passed\n+\n+Checklist\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: issue reviewed and scope identified\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology verified clean before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: not needed beyond issue-provided EC/RHEA guidance for this batch\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: affected terms and comparable parent classes inspected in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: reaction-term precedent reviewed; no new logical definitions added\n+- [x] EDITS: used checkout/checkin workflow via `terms/`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: corrected asserted `is_a` parentage to match EC subclasses\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: `/reaction` consulted\n+- [x] METADATA: preserved existing metadata and added issue tracker links for this curation pass\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: used existing/issue-specified RHEA references only\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: ontology changes committed locally\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Summary:\n+- corrected EC-driven parentage for a batch of oxidoreductase activity terms in the catalytic activity branch\n+- updated several reaction definitions to align with current RHEA reactions\n+- renamed terms where the existing label no longer matched the enzyme class/reaction\n+\n+Validated locally with `make travis_build`.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,58 @@\n+This PR addresses issue #31969 by correcting a batch of oxidoreductase catalytic activity terms whose asserted parentage did not match their EC subclass, and by updating several reaction definitions/labels to better align with RHEA.\n+\n+Main changes\n+\n+- Reparented EC:1.17.1 terms to `GO:0016726` and the EC:1.17.2 term to `GO:0016725`:\n+  - `GO:0008863` formate dehydrogenase (NAD+) activity\n+  - `GO:0047899` formate dehydrogenase (NADP+) activity\n+  - `GO:0008839` 4-hydroxy-tetrahydrodipicolinate reductase activity\n+  - `GO:0047111` formate dehydrogenase (cytochrome-c-553) activity\n+\n+- Corrected CH-OH / CH-CH / CH-NH branch placement:\n+  - `GO:0050607` reparented to `GO:0016616` and renamed to `S-(hydroxymethyl)mycothiol dehydrogenase activity`\n+  - `GO:0008762` reparented to `GO:0016628`\n+  - `GO:0018525` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+  - `GO:0044684` reparented to `GO:0016645`\n+  - `GO:0033717` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+\n+- Corrected oxygenase/dioxygenase parentage in the 1.14 branch:\n+  - `GO:0102394` renamed to `L-isoleucine 4-hydroxylase activity` and reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0047081` renamed to `3-hydroxy-2-methylpyridine-5-carboxylate monooxygenase [NAD(P)H] activity` and reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0106145` reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0010277` reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0050588` reparented to `GO:0016702`\n+  - `GO:0033759`, `GO:0045431`, `GO:0047594`, `GO:0050589` reparented to `GO:0050498`\n+  - `GO:0102717` reparented from `GO:0050498` to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0050616` and `GO:0102915` reparented to `GO:0016717`\n+  - `GO:0032441`, `GO:0004498`, and `GO:0036199` reparented to `GO:0016713`\n+  - `GO:0018570` reparented to `GO:0016708`\n+\n+- Updated reaction definitions to current RHEA-aligned wording where requested, including:\n+  - `GO:0050607`, `GO:0008762`, `GO:0018525`, `GO:0044684`, `GO:0047081`, `GO:0106145`, `GO:0102717`, `GO:0050616`, `GO:0102915`, `GO:0032441`\n+\n+- Added `term_tracker_item` links to issue `#31969` on all edited terms.\n+\n+Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before edits:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+\n+- Post-edit validation:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+  - `robot reason -r ELK -i go-edit.obo -o /tmp/opencode/go-edit.reasoned.obo` passed\n+  - `make travis_build` passed\n+\n+Checklist\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: issue reviewed and scope identified\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology verified clean before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: not needed beyond issue-provided EC/RHEA guidance for this batch\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: affected terms and comparable parent classes inspected in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: reaction-term precedent reviewed; no new logical definitions added\n+- [x] EDITS: used checkout/checkin workflow via `terms/`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: corrected asserted `is_a` parentage to match EC subclasses\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: `/reaction` consulted\n+- [x] METADATA: preserved existing metadata and added issue tracker links for this curation pass\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: used existing/issue-specified RHEA references only\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: ontology changes committed locally\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Summary:\n+- corrected EC-driven parentage for a batch of oxidoreductase activity terms in the catalytic activity branch\n+- updated several reaction definitions to align with current RHEA reactions\n+- renamed terms where the existing label no longer matched the enzyme class/reaction\n+\n+Validated locally with `make travis_build`.\n","additions":8,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,58 @@\n+This PR addresses issue #31969 by correcting a batch of oxidoreductase catalytic activity terms whose asserted parentage did not match their EC subclass, and by updating several reaction definitions/labels to better align with RHEA.\n+\n+Main changes\n+\n+- Reparented EC:1.17.1 terms to `GO:0016726` and the EC:1.17.2 term to `GO:0016725`:\n+  - `GO:0008863` formate dehydrogenase (NAD+) activity\n+  - `GO:0047899` formate dehydrogenase (NADP+) activity\n+  - `GO:0008839` 4-hydroxy-tetrahydrodipicolinate reductase activity\n+  - `GO:0047111` formate dehydrogenase (cytochrome-c-553) activity\n+\n+- Corrected CH-OH / CH-CH / CH-NH branch placement:\n+  - `GO:0050607` reparented to `GO:0016616` and renamed to `S-(hydroxymethyl)mycothiol dehydrogenase activity`\n+  - `GO:0008762` reparented to `GO:0016628`\n+  - `GO:0018525` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+  - `GO:0044684` reparented to `GO:0016645`\n+  - `GO:0033717` reparented to `GO:0016614`\n+\n+- Corrected oxygenase/dioxygenase parentage in the 1.14 branch:\n+  - `GO:0102394` renamed to `L-isoleucine 4-hydroxylase activity` and reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0047081` renamed to `3-hydroxy-2-methylpyridine-5-carboxylate monooxygenase [NAD(P)H] activity` and reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0106145` reparented to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0010277` reparented to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0050588` reparented to `GO:0016702`\n+  - `GO:0033759`, `GO:0045431`, `GO:0047594`, `GO:0050589` reparented to `GO:0050498`\n+  - `GO:0102717` reparented from `GO:0050498` to `GO:0016706`\n+  - `GO:0050616` and `GO:0102915` reparented to `GO:0016717`\n+  - `GO:0032441`, `GO:0004498`, and `GO:0036199` reparented to `GO:0016713`\n+  - `GO:0018570` reparented to `GO:0016708`\n+\n+- Updated reaction definitions to current RHEA-aligned wording where requested, including:\n+  - `GO:0050607`, `GO:0008762`, `GO:0018525`, `GO:0044684`, `GO:0047081`, `GO:0106145`, `GO:0102717`, `GO:0050616`, `GO:0102915`, `GO:0032441`\n+\n+- Added `term_tracker_item` links to issue `#31969` on all edited terms.\n+\n+Validation\n+\n+- Pre-validation before edits:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+\n+- Post-edit validation:\n+  - `robot verify -i go-edit.obo --queries ...` passed\n+  - `robot reason -r ELK -i go-edit.obo -o /tmp/opencode/go-edit.reasoned.obo` passed\n+  - `make travis_build` passed\n+\n+Checklist\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: issue reviewed and scope identified\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology verified clean before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: not needed beyond issue-provided EC/RHEA guidance for this batch\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: affected terms and comparable parent classes inspected in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: reaction-term precedent reviewed; no new logical definitions added\n+- [x] EDITS: used checkout/checkin workflow via `terms/`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: corrected asserted `is_a` parentage to match EC subclasses\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: `/reaction` consulted\n+- [x] METADATA: preserved existing metadata and added issue tracker links for this curation pass\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: used existing/issue-specified RHEA references only\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: ontology changes committed locally\n","additions":58,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778991803302,"end":1778991803311}},"id":"prt_e342c5173001pcH7o8FRL7364g","sessionID":"ses_1cbe49278ffeRFVub9JhoaSOUZ","messageID":"msg_e342c484d001S4FqTCs8Jn7C4Q"}}
